{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"223330-the-little-plant","title":"The Little Plant","description":"Look closely at the plants around you, there is so much to see, so many creatures to meet, and so much to learn! ","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Radha Rangarajan"],"illustrators":["Aindri C"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/223330-the-little-plant"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/715981/size3/10130d05074d4687484c87f23e820b1b.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/715981/size6/10130d05074d4687484c87f23e820b1b.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/313363/size6/279d0d8b6cb562d0fee2cc99e8cbccfe.jpg","text":"2/10","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/313364/size6/0e692ccdc526269e4989566187fdcc50.jpg","text":"3/10","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/337302/size6/d9ed3d9cb3cbf59e9a81a56c3c29af71.jpg","text":"4/10","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/337307/size6/9735d85de28ef824f52ac2ad13b3b2c8.jpg","text":"5/10","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/337309/size6/b56065282fc3cfe04c64e25732cf5b83.jpg","text":"6/10","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/337312/size6/b374c19c25e72362fcda697c8459fa2e.jpg","text":"7/10","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/313826/size6/47dac6a783657118e17b20cca97cb24e.jpg","text":"Parts of a plant\nLook at a plant closely. Its roots are below the soil. Its leaves, flowers and fruits grow on the stem, above the soil. Here are the main parts of a plant —\nSeeds\nFlower\nFruit\nLeaf\nStem\nRoots","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/313827/size6/f99a28be499cb750fa8c479bbbe8c817.jpg","text":"All plants are home to many forms of life like worms, insects and spiders.\nAnts and Aphids are often seen together on plants.\nEarthworms live around\nthe roots and keep the soil healthy.\nLeafcutter Bees use pieces of leaves to build their nests.\nLeafcutter Bee\nAnt\nAphid\nAnt Larva\nEarthworm","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/313828/size6/bfe74a8ddb648bd53c393527fbdf4652.jpg","text":"10/10","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":9,"words":99}}